    proclaim: "The [bold cyan]Active Shield[/bold cyan] Zenith Gate is manifest."
    proclaim: "Stateless Defense: [white]core/security/shield.py[/]"
    proclaim: "Protection Layer: [bold green]ZENITH (Line Zero)[/]"
    proclaim: "LIF-Multiplier: [bold green]10,000x (Ingress Latency -> 0ms)[/]"

